definition: Bulgaria/Bulgarian/abbr. for 保加利亞|保加利亚[Bao3 jia1 li4 ya4]
to defend/to protect/to keep/to guarantee/to ensure/civil administration unit in the baojia 保甲[bao3 jia3] system (old)
to have/there is/there are/to exist/to be

sentences.english: I want to keep that trust.
He may retain his human dignity even in a concentration camp.
sentences.chinese: 即使是置身於集中營，他仍可以保有他的人性尊嚴。

sentences.english: It also has a “whole lot of planes” to keep in the air, as she puts it.
sentences.chinese: 她指出，亞航也保有“一大批的飛機”在運營中。

sentences.english: The bank says it keeps plenty of liquid reserves against the dread day.
sentences.chinese: 銀行聲稱他保有大量流動儲備以應對恐懼日的到來。

sentences.english: The first chapter deals with issues of timeliness and having a positive mental attitude.
sentences.chinese: 第一章解決的是時間和保有積極態度的問題。

sentences.english: Nice to hear that Mayweather hasn't lost his competitive edge.
sentences.chinese: 很高興聽到梅威瑟仍舊保有他的競爭優勢。

sentences.english: First, we must postulate that if souls exist, they must have some mass.
sentences.chinese: 第一，我們必須假定靈魂存在，他們必須保有物質。

sentences.english: Mody? We must maintain an integrity of nature and a pure heart.
sentences.chinese: 麼？我們一定要保有一顆完整的本性和一顆清淨的心。

sentences.english: Jesus forgives all of us that repents of their sin.
sentences.chinese: 耶穌赦免全人類，雖然人類保有原罪。

sentences.english: On current form, Linke deserves to retain his Germany place.
sentences.chinese: 就現在的狀態來說，林克應當保有國家隊的位置。

sentences.english: Ensure family in Jin Guoqing previous fight against each other edge is always maintained.
sentences.chinese: 保證了其在晉國卿族的歷次互相爭鬥中始終保有優勢。

sentences.english: CIMA reserves the rights to adjust the agenda.
sentences.chinese: CIMA保有對議程進行調整的權利。

sentences.english: Every adult still remains a child somewhere deep in his or her soul.
sentences.chinese: 每個成年人無不在內心深處保有一份童真。

sentences.english: The Institute Organizing Committee reserves the right to assign hotels based on a first-come-first-served basis.
sentences.chinese: 研習會籌備委員會保有權利，對先到先服務之原則。

sentences.english: But the group appeared to retain some support among Gaza residents.
sentences.chinese: 不過這個集團似乎還保有一些加沙居民的支持。

sentences.english: Your plan can also have some flexibility.
sentences.chinese: 投資計畫也需保有一些彈性。

to hold fast to/to stick to
